{"tid":885022,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劇透！下一部《黑天鵝》？Natalie Portman 8年後再度挑戰黑暗人格角色，網民：當年睇佢搣手指睇到起雞皮！","createTime":"2018-11-01T04:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T02:18:00.000Z","uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"345ff0712f8e7e18bdfa5f7fb311f29b2f8bc246","tid":885022,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">下一部《黑天鵝》？Natalie Portman 8年後再度挑戰黑暗人格角色，網民：當年睇佢搣手指睇到起雞皮！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n提到Natalie Portman這位奧斯卡影后，相信不少人都會想起她多年前的經典名作《黑天鵝》(Black Swan)，當年她完美地詮釋劇中女舞者的複雜心理，一人分飾兩角，展現可怕的人性黑暗，絕對令人拍案叫絕～想不到時隔8年後，Natalie Portman又要再度挑戰難度極高的人格分裂角色！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/33a95e1cd1ba83e91127f25c4e531acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F33a95e1cd1ba83e91127f25c4e531acb.jpg&h=155bcdea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《黑天鵝》這部驚悚劇情片於當年上映後引來不少哄動，觀眾們都被Natalie Portman所分飾的「白天鵝」及「黑天鵝」的魅力所吸引，「白天鵝」温馴乖巧，聽從母親的指令，但其實心底裏卻長期受到壓抑～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1fc890d91caeb00ac1e6e8f3efb8d179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1fc890d91caeb00ac1e6e8f3efb8d179.jpg&h=32303167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「黑天鵝」則是把這壓抑的情緒釋放，徹底展現人性的黑暗～能夠成功詮釋兩種擁有截然不同個性的角色，也充分奠定了她奧斯卡影后的地位～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ec4bccd64399ee59aba3fc11bac6d035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fec4bccd64399ee59aba3fc11bac6d035.jpg&h=529ea843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今次Natalie Portman於新作品《Vox Lux》(光之聲)中將飾演一位曾經歷校園槍擊事件後成長的流行樂壇巨星Celeste，她因為槍擊事件受害者的角色在偶然的機會下因此「成名」，以動人的歌聲成為正面激勵人心的象徵，更因此名成利就！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-10-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.12.27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-10-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.12.27.jpg&h=94ca2dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-10-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.12.53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-10-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.12.53.jpg&h=74e14ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過隨著歲月的流逝，Celeste即使站在舞台熾熱的光芒下，接受萬千粉絲的歡呼掌聲，可是這樣一個耀眼的她卻原來一直未能從過去的陰霾中走出來～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-10-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.30.36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-10-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.30.36.jpg&h=fb4c1e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-10-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.32.12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-10-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.32.12.jpg&h=099c81ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCeleste的心靈早已被過去承受的巨大心理創傷折磨得體無完膚，性格變得扭曲，外表看似正常，但內心卻是憤世嫉俗～一次重回家鄉開個唱不幸再次遇上槍擊事件，就觸發她內心長久以來的不安及壓抑，隱藏在深處的惡魔人格開始逐步展現&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n從劇組釋出的劇照及預告所見，Natalie Portman一改平日高貴典雅的形象，穿上搖滾味濃的帥氣龐克服，化上舞台感重的煙燻妝，魅力四射，宛如真正的樂壇天后！而據知Natalie Portman於電影中亦真的會演唱多首歌曲，她將以何樣細膩的演技靈活詮釋這位角色的確令人心生期待～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-10-30-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.41.50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-10-30-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.41.50.jpg&h=fb2f5815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/928026506-594x594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdfi5wu8thl82p.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F928026506-594x594.jpg&h=006a9687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此部電影早前已經在威尼斯影展進行世界首映，不少人都覺得Natalie Portman有機會再度憑此角色入圍奧斯卡提名，電影預計將在12月7日於美國上映，大家也可密切留意香港的上映日期喔～<br />\n現在就來看一看電影《Vox Lux》的預告片吧～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dolxUIZzb3w#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdolxUIZzb3w%23&d=AKjg2iWHSuq2wjL7IOPsHYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=477a902d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dolxUIZzb3w#</a>"},{"pid":"9603f73ceb6a191ca43b37cae9fbced61817302a","tid":885022,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d61d17b93987c2d14412ec337e4a5b99254fa87","tid":885022,"uid":32282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0eaed285bdd5dc70695f89251e8d66a7b56eb99","tid":885022,"uid":140979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032c3974f56ec3a013e9a7f1379c41039e1384db","tid":885022,"uid":2772,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Am4puE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAm4puE7.jpg&h=22b71507&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27dd5f304025513179d08d427e70dc77572d4d5c","tid":885022,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"其實覺得黑天鵝好普通"},{"pid":"2de5002472b6cd4e3d56e339b99d0a4457d741c7","tid":885022,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27dd5f304025513179d08d427e70dc77572d4d5c","tid":885022,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"其實覺得黑天鵝好普通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"剪接 劇本 演技 攝影都好喎<br />\n<br />\n係個氣氛好陰沈所以睇到個人好辛苦姐"},{"pid":"7c2943d11b58234c7abf73e6f8425ba2df305687","tid":885022,"uid":22364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2de5002472b6cd4e3d56e339b99d0a4457d741c7","tid":885022,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27dd5f304025513179d08d427e70dc77572d4d5c","tid":885022,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"其實覺得黑天鵝好普通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"剪接 劇本 演技 攝影都好喎<br />\n<br />\n係個氣氛好陰沈所以睇到個人好辛苦姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"佢營造出黎個種氣氛真係到有抖唔到氣既感覺"},{"pid":"189c54a52282b8ba8eca842249ace74cfe74f9ac","tid":885022,"uid":54812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"條trailer 一啲都唔吸引"},{"pid":"9d3116c3964fc0c1b626f49b63d82cf91f28ba00","tid":885022,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"Portman Portman Portman Portman"},{"pid":"19141f9b54e0c99b12a9b97c9e0fc93ed31d4141","tid":885022,"uid":74778,"l